of pictures that he had taken, being one of the 
great pioneers of photography and astronomy and

39:21.119 --> 39:33.611
discoverer of comets and whatnot, and the fifth 
satellite of Jupiter. He was a well-known

39:33.671 --> 39:43.240
personality, but he didn't write popular books 
and didn't have the same charisma, contacts, and

39:33.671 --> 39:43.240
persona that Percival Lowell did. Percival 
