45:48.394 --> 45:58.202
discovered that this was spurious because the 
interferometer control system used a helium

45:48.394 --> 45:58.202
lamp. to provide the clocking frequency. And 
while we could not imagine how this Spiria signal

46:03.298 --> 46:09.805
got into the signal chain, indeed it did. And our 
detection of helium on Io was wrong. And Larry

46:13.770 --> 46:21.138
Trafton continues to remind me of that, even 
though the rest of the world until this very moment

46:13.770 --> 46:21.138
has forgotten, mercifully forgotten. If you read 
any of the popular books about exploration of the

46:24.457 --> 46:30.144
solar system that have been coming out in the last 
20 years. It's all done by the space probes. Of

46:32.307 --> 46:32.688
course. What's your opinion? My opinion is that 
the space probes wouldn't have even known where to

46:35.111 --> 46:44.964
go or what to look at or how to look at it if it hadn't 
been for the work that has been done on the ground.

46:45.524 --> 46:52.253
And certainly the incremental improvement in our 
understanding of the planets was enormously

46:45.524 --> 46:52.253
augmented by the space probes. space probes. But 
